---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Short Films / AI Experiments" showFooter={false} dark={true}>
  <article class="project">
    <!-- ── Row 1: Header and Hero Video ── -->
    <div class="project-grid">
      <div class="project-cards">
        <div class="card card--tag">
          <span>SHORT FILMS / AI EXPERIMENTS</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--title">
          <h1 class="project-title">Short Films & AI Experiments</h1>
          <div class="project-subtitle">
            <p>
              This section presents a series of short films created as part of
              the thesis project, together with additional independent footage
              reworked through artificial intelligence tools. Through image,
              sound, editing, and visual experimentation, the videos explore the
              mind as an unstable and fragmented space.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--body">
          <p>
            The short films act as a practical extension of the research,
            investigating perception, identity, memory, and the distortion of
            reality. Some of the footage, although not directly connected to the
            main thesis project, was later transformed using AI tools in order
            to experiment with new visual possibilities and demonstrate a
            contemporary approach to digital image-making.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer"></div>

        <div class="card card--tag">
          <span>Hybrid Archive</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--body card--upper">
          <p>
            The result is a hybrid visual archive where cinema, editing, and
            artificial intelligence interact, showing the project’s ability to
            move between narrative, artistic research, and technological
            experimentation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-hero">
        <video src="/images/work/05/05-01.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="none"
        ></video>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Row 2: Gallery of 2 Videos ── -->
    <div class="project-gallery">
      <div class="video-wrap">
        <video src="/images/work/05/05-02.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="none"
        ></video>
      </div>
      <div class="video-wrap">
        <video src="/images/work/05/05-03.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="none"
        ></video>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Row 3: Asymmetric layout for last 2 videos ── -->
    <div class="gallery-asymmetric">
      <video src="/images/work/05/05-04.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="none"
      ></video>
      <video src="/images/work/05/05-05.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="none"
      ></video>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  /* ── Page shell ── */
  .project {
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 96px;
  }

  /* ── Row 1: grid ── */
  .project-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 24px 24px 10px;
  }

  .project-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .card {
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
  }

  .card--tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    align-self: flex-start;
    padding: 8px 14px;
  }
  .card--tag span {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .spacer {
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 16px;
  }

  .card--title {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .project-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    flex: 0 0 44%;
    padding-right: 20px;
  }
  .project-subtitle {
    flex: 1;
    border-left: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .project-subtitle p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .card--body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .card--upper p {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .project-hero {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: #000;
  }
  .project-hero video {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-height: 600px;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── Row 2: Gallery of 2 videos ── */
  .project-gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 10px 24px;
  }
  .project-gallery video {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .video-wrap {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #000;
  }

  .video-wrap video {
    object-fit: contain;
    max-height: 600px;
  }

  /* ── Row 3: Asymmetric layout ── */
  .gallery-asymmetric {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    grid-auto-rows: 380px;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 10px 24px 48px;
  }
  .gallery-asymmetric video {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: #000;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .project-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .project-hero {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .project {
      padding-top: 88px;
    }

    .project-grid {
      padding: 16px 16px 8px;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .project-gallery,
    .gallery-asymmetric {
      padding: 8px 16px;
    }
    .project-gallery {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .gallery-asymmetric {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .card--title {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .project-subtitle {
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      padding-left: 0;
      padding-top: 12px;
    }
    .spacer {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
